SELECT MAX(oMonetaryAmount."HASAMOUNT") AS AggResult1 FROM "FIBEN"."LISTEDSECURITY" AS oListedSecurity INNER JOIN "FIBEN"."MONETARYAMOUNT" AS oMonetaryAmount ON oListedSecurity."HASLASTTRADEDVALUE" = oMonetaryAmount."MONETARYAMOUNTID" INNER JOIN "FIBEN"."SECURITY" AS Security1 ON oListedSecurity."LISTEDSECURITYID" = Security1."SECURITYID" INNER JOIN "FIBEN"."FINANCIALMARKET" AS oFinancialMarket ON Security1."ISTRADEDON" = oFinancialMarket."FINANCIALMARKETID" WHERE oFinancialMarket."HASNAME" = 'NYSE'